om\": 249, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP Two-time Olympic gold medalist weightlifter Shi Zhiyong of China will compete for his third title at the coming 2024 Summer Olympic Games that will begin on July 26 in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Zhiyong_(weightlifter,_born_1980)\", \"score\": 0.8421034060992093, \"rank\": 0.18750000000000883, \"text\": \"Shi Zhiyong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Zhiyong_(weightlifter,_born_1980)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Zhiyong_(weightlifter,_born_1980)\"}, {\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9805240904135558, \"rank\": 0.017521783558816142, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999931253569, \"rank\": 6.874680366343914e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.680533032865137, \"rank\": 0.30224056619702017, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his third title\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming 2024 Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, the 30-year-old veteran will have more difficulties to overcome.When Shi broke the world record to win the weightlifting men's 73-kilogram gold at the Tokyo Olympic Games in 2021, he yelled \\\"Who wants to challenge me!\\\"\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 30-year-old veteran\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"more difficulties\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"Shi\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"the weightlifting men's 73-kilogram gold\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"with excitement and authority.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"authority\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, not many knew that he had been dealing with various injuries before that moment.Having aged in the following years, injuries began to have a bigger effect on Shi, especially by costing him regular and systematic training sessions and practice.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"various injuries\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"the following years\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"a bigger effect\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"Shi\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"regular and systematic training sessions\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, he has not appeared in many international events since then.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"many international events\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"se